            <h2>History </h2><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Artichoke_dip&action=edit&section=2"><small>[edit]</small></a>
            
            <hr />

            <p>Spinach and Artichoke dip became prominent in the 50s when eating in front of the TV became more common. These became widespread as they do not require any utensils. Consumer Packaged Goods companies like Lays, Hellman's and Lipton's helped push this trend.</p>


